    {
        "content": "<p>No, it is still there, it just moved. I think we can do this:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Rust\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"n\">diff</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">--</span><span class=\"n\">git</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">rust</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">kernel</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">module_param</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">rs</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">b</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">rust</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">kernel</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">module_param</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">rs</span>\n<span class=\"n\">index</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">e7d5c930a467d</span><span class=\"o\">..</span><span class=\"mi\">6</span><span class=\"n\">a8a7a875643a</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">100644</span>\n<span class=\"o\">---</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">rust</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">kernel</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">module_param</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">rs</span>\n<span class=\"o\">+++</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">b</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">rust</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">kernel</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">module_param</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">rs</span>\n<span class=\"o\">@@</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"mi\">70</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"mi\">6</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">+</span><span class=\"mi\">70</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"mi\">7</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">@@</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">pub</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">trait</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">ModuleParam</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nb\">Sized</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">+</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nb\">Copy</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">     </span><span class=\"c1\">// SAFETY: By function safety requirement, val is non-null, null-terminated</span>\n<span class=\"w\">     </span><span class=\"c1\">// and valid for reads for the duration of this function.</span>\n<span class=\"w\">     </span><span class=\"kd\">let</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">arg</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">unsafe</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">CStr</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">from_char_ptr</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">val</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">};</span>\n<span class=\"o\">+</span><span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"kd\">let</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">arg</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kp\">&amp;</span><span class=\"nc\">BStr</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">arg</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">as_ref</span><span class=\"p\">();</span>\n\n<span class=\"w\">     </span><span class=\"k\">crate</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">error</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">from_result</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"o\">||</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">         </span><span class=\"kd\">let</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">new_value</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">T</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">try_from_param_arg</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">arg</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"o\">?</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
